'''Amḍan''' iga tagrumma n yan nɣ kigan n izwilen. Imḍanen d tiɣawsiwin n [[tusnakt]].
==Tigrummiwin n imḍanen==
Llan ɣ tusnakt sḍist tgrummiwin n imḍanen, ɣwid ad-tn igan :
* Tagrumma '''N''' ( nɣ <math display="inline">\mathbb{N}\,</math>) n [[Ummid agaman|ummidn igamann]], nna ɣ nttafa imḍanen nzḍar ad-tn ntara s izwilen, s umdya : 0, 1, 2, 3 ... ;
* Tagrumma '''Z''' ( nɣ <math>\mathbb{Z}\,</math>) n [[Ummid amaqqan|ummidn imaqqann]], nna ɣ nttafa imḍanen uzdirn (<math>+</math>) ula willi ganin umnign (<math>-</math>) ;
* Tagrumma '''D''' ( nɣ <math>\mathbb{D}\,</math>) n [[Amḍan amrawan|imḍanen imrawann]], nna ɣ nttafa imḍanen darsn yat tafult tga tummidt, tiss-snat tga tamrawant ur dars tmi, gr tifulin ad ar nttara yat tiskrt ;
* Tagrumma '''Q''' ( nɣ <math>\mathbb Q</math>) n [[Amḍan amɣẓan|imḍanen imɣẓann]], nna ɣ nttafa imḍanen nzḍar ad-tn ntara s tarfiqt gis yan uzwil ɣ uflla d wayyaḍ ɣ izddar, izwiln ad s sin iqqand ad gin imnza gr-atsn ;
* Tagrumma '''R''' ( nɣ <math>\mathbb{R}\,</math>) n [[Amḍan ilaw|imḍanen ilawn]], nna ɣ nttafa imḍanen imɣẓann ula willi t ur ganin ;
* Tagrumma '''C''' ( nɣ <math display="inline">\mathbb{C}\,</math>) n [[Amḍan asmlal|imḍanen ismlaln]], nna ɣ nttafa imḍanen darsn yat tafult tga tilawt, tiss-snat tga tasugnant.
S ɣmk-ad nzḍar ad nfk ayda yad :
:<math>\mathbb{N}\sub\mathbb{Z}\sub\mathbb{D}\sub\mathbb{Q}\sub\mathbb{R}\sub\mathbb{C}</math>

